                        The Fujifilm X-S20 represents exceptional value at $1,299. By incorporating 6.2K video, 5-axis IBIS, subject detection AF, and Film Simulations into a compact body, Fujifilm has created the ultimate hybrid camera for content creators and enthusiast photographers.
