                        The 26MP X-Trans sensor delivers exceptional sharpness with Fujifilm's signature color science. With 19 Film Simulations including Velvia and Classic Chrome, you get stunning JPEG files straight out of camera. Dynamic range is approximately 13 stops at base ISO.
