                        Video is where the X-S20 truly shines. 6.2K 30p with 10-bit 4:2:2 internal provides exceptional grading flexibility. FHD 240fps enables dramatic slow motion. Heat management is excellentâ€”continuous 4K 60p for 90+ minutes without overheating.
                    </p>
